# Habit House

Habit House is an AI-powered life operating system that automates personal growth.

## Vision
To remove friction from self-improvement by turning habits, goals, and routines into an intelligent automated system.

## Core Idea
Users don’t manually track life anymore. AI handles it.

## MVP Features
- AI onboarding
- Daily habit dashboard
- Smart habit tracking
- AI coaching system
- Weekly performance review

## Tech Direction
- Frontend: FlutterFlow (mobile app)
- Backend: Firebase
- AI: OpenAI API
- Analytics: Firebase Analytics

## Long Term Vision
A personal AI assistant that manages health, productivity, learning, and goals automatically.
